{{Y|Press [{{W|Help}}] while in quick menu for help.}}

{{W|* App restart is required after approving or enabling this mod from disabled state, or it might cause the game to freeze. If that's the case, simply Alt+F4 and restart the game.}}
{{w|* If you are experiencing dark color main menu after restart, as far as I'm concerned it's safe to ignore.}}
{{W|* To access quick menu screen, assign a key to open quick menu in the [Quick Menu] section from Key Mapping.}}

This mod adds a new menu which acts as a hub to ties all status screens into one keymap.
Main purpose is to free up some keymaps for no-numpad user or anyone who think their keymap is a mess (aka me for both cases).
